## Show site settings


> Example Request

```shell--json
curl https://app.files.com/api/rest/v1/site.json \
  -H 'X-FilesAPI-Key: YOUR_API_KEY'
```

```shell--xml
curl https://app.files.com/api/rest/v1/site.xml \
  -H 'X-FilesAPI-Key: YOUR_API_KEY'
```

```ruby
Files.api_key = 'YOUR_API_KEY'

Files::Site.get
```

```php
\Files\Files::setApiKey('YOUR_API_KEY');

\Files\Site::get();
```

